{"tid":1366512,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碼頭咕哩古圖斯：人人都清楚知道我才是皇馬首席門神","createTime":"2019-07-26T03:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T12:46:41.000Z","uid":165817,"like":3,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9185453a204df5d8d0b4c5b08f8642dda6f5d50a","tid":1366512,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里門將古圖斯最近接受了專訪，他在訪問中他，表示大家都很清楚誰是球隊的一號門將。<br />\n<br />\n古圖斯表示：「我很注意自己的身體，上季結束時，我的脂肪含量是百分之八點八，而現在已經降到了八點一。我覺得自己比以往更強壯，在度過了一個月的假期來說，這是很難得的。」<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，現在我們清楚的知道，誰才是一號門將，我感覺我比以往任何時候都更強大。」"},{"pid":"1c46f6c5c61d88f15c63877e683921209a0638d8","tid":1366512,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6e75abba1abc19e2ebdb9fae98ee4dea41ee8e","tid":1366512,"uid":87155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6950fe19f78fe5dcef5b50fe93a11f936d0fabd3","tid":1366512,"uid":15915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"死得其所"},{"pid":"bde5f20d1c3ad9cae6607a12958ff2ca9acfd216","tid":1366512,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3b8f2f3130cbf7fa8acf8fb6bbabfb26c6